Hello all,


When reflecting the interfaces of a class, I get strange key names for
the classes:

8<------------------
array(5) {
  ["GtkTreeMode"]=>
  &object(ReflectionClass)#33 (1) {
    ["name"]=>
    string(12) "GtkTreeModel"
